quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,"Menen Men wee…ìinanii mo ka leydi, Men Jonni mo e kala huunde nde o …óa…ì…ìata laawol hewtinayngol mo e faandaare makko."
  18,85,"O nanngi ko Men Okki mo kon immorde e laawi fii hewtugol e …óa…ì…ìaande makko, o sutori hirnaange."
  18,86,"O yahi ka leydi haa o hewti ka hattirde leydi ndin ka hella mutirde naange, o yi'i nge awiima kannge hinge muta e caangol wulungol wonndungol e loope …ìaleeje, o tawi ka mutirde naange ngen yim…ìe heefer…ìe, Men wi'ani mo e hoore su…ìinngol mo: "Ko an yo jom galaa…ói …ói…ói, ko si a leptiray …ìee warugol maa tanaa mun, maa…óun si a mo∆¥∆¥oto e ma…ì…ìe."
  18,87,"Jom gallaa…ói …óin …ói…ói wi'i: "Si tawii ko on sirkan…óo Alla o deppitii(doonii) e sirku ngun …ìaawo men noddii mo e dewal, men leptiray mo ka aduna warugol, refti o ruttoo ka Joomi makko √ëalnde Darngal O Lepta mo Lepte hul…ìinii…óe"."
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gom…óin…óo e ma…ì…ìe Alla o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i no woodani mo Aljanna; njo…ódi immorde ka Joomi makko sabu gom…óinal makko ngal e golle makko mo∆¥∆¥e …óen, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen ko wonndi e newaare."
  18,89,"Refti o jokki laawol tanaa laawol makko aranol ngol ko o fewtir…óo hella funnaange."
  18,90,"O yahi haa nde o hewtoynoo e nokkuure nde naange ngen ∆¥ellitotoo e mun, o tawi naange ngen no ∆¥ellitoo e dow yim…ìe Men wa…óanaali …ìe gaanin naange ngen ko hiwata …ìe wano cuu…ói e …óowdiiji le…ó…óe."
  18,91,"Ko wano nii fiyaake jom gallaa…ói …óin …ói…ói, gom…óii o fiiltiima ganndal e fennsitale ko woni kon ka makko e doole e laamu."
  18,92,"Refti o jokki laawol tanaa laawi arani …óin …ói…ói ko o falor…óo hakkunde funnaange e hirnaange."
  18,93,"O yahi haa o hewti yolnde hakkunde pelle …ói…ói, o tawi fewndo mayre yim…ìe …ìe mee…óaa faamude haala wo…ì…ìe goo."
  18,94,"∆Åe wi'i: "Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja (…ìen ko moftaaji …ói…ói maw…ói e …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama) hi…ìe bonirde ka leydi ko …ìe woni wa…óude kon immorde e warngo e tanaa mun. Taw si men wa…óante jawdi fii yo a wa…óu hakkunde e ma…ì…ìe heedo?""
  18,95,"Julqarnayni wi'i: "Ko Joomi am arsiki lam kon e laamu e doole …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde lam diini gaa ko jonnoton lam e jawdi, walliree lam wor…ìe e aalaaji mi wa…óa hakkunde mo'on e ma…ì…ìe heedo"."
  18,96,"Addee kunte njam…óe, …ìe addi …óum o nanngi mahirgol …óe hakkunde pelle …óen …ói…ói, haa nde o feppindirirnoo hakkunde majje maadi makko ndin o wi'ani golloo…ìe …ìen: "Hu…ì…ìinee yiite e dow …óe'e kunte, haa nde kunte njam…óe …óen wojjunoo o wi'i: "Addee sila mi yuppa e dow mun."
  18,97,"Yaajuuja e Maajuuja hattantaake ∆¥awugol e hoore maadi ndin sabu toowugol mayri, …ìe hattantaake kadi tufugol ka ley mayri sabu yoorugol mayri."